OL,3,CWould you move to this 'tiny island'
OL,4,Cto play football at The Arsenal?
OL,6,FFor aspiring footballers, a change of
OL,7,Fclub might mean travelling to a new
OL,8,Fcity or even moving countries, but
OL,9,Fwould you consider relocating to a
OL,10,F"tiny island" in the English Channel?
OL,12,FAlderney has a population of around
OL,13,F2,000 and struggles with a shortage of
OL,14,Fyoung men to play for the island's
OL,15,Fonly football team.
