OL,3,CWould you move to this 'tiny island'
OL,4,Cto play football at The Arsenal?
OL,6,FAlderney FC is nicknamed The Nomads
OL,7,Fand wants that spirit to be adopted by
OL,8,Ffootballers living in the other
OL,9,FChannel Islands, the UK, and beyond,
OL,10,Fso they can put forward a competitive
OL,11,Fteam for Guernsey's Priaulx League.
OL,13,FThey also play in the Channel Islands'
OL,14,Fshowpiece annual tournament, the
OL,15,FMuratti Vase, competing against Jersey
OL,16,Fand Guernsey for footballing glory.
OL,18,FAlderney has only beaten its much
OL,19,Flarger neighbours once in 1920, but
OL,20,Fhopes fresh momentum will build
OL,21,Ffurther memories.
