OL,3,CWould you move to this 'tiny island'
OL,4,Cto play football at The Arsenal?
OL,6,FChairman and team coach, Rob Kirkland,
OL,7,Fsays: "We hope that we offer a little
OL,8,Fslice of paradise here on the island,
OL,9,Fan incredibly well-run club supported
OL,10,Fby the community.
OL,12,F"We have to do everything we can to
OL,13,Ffill that void. We have 10 competitive
OL,14,Fmen based on the island, but we need a
OL,15,Flarger squad to be able to compete in
OL,16,Fthe Guernsey leagues."
