OL,3,CWould you move to this 'tiny island'
OL,4,Cto play football at The Arsenal?
OL,6,FThe campaign for new footballers
OL,7,Fstarted a couple of weeks ago as the
OL,8,Fteam declared in a social media post
OL,9,Fthat "on a tiny island in the English
OL,10,FChannel, Alderney's football club is
OL,11,Fdoing something different".
OL,13,FIt added you can "live on an island
OL,14,Fthat looks like a David Attenborough
OL,15,Fdocumentary" and "play your guts out
OL,16,Ffor a team that actually needs you".
OL,18,FRob says the post has got traction
OL,19,Fwith tens of thousands of views, and
OL,20,Fhe is encouraged by the early signs.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G4/7
