OL,3,CWould you move to this 'tiny island'
OL,4,Cto play football at The Arsenal?
OL,6,FHe explains: "A number of players have
OL,7,Fexpressed an interest in relocating,
OL,8,Fand we're in initial discussions.
OL,10,F"We've also had a number of agents
OL,11,Finterested in bringing players across
OL,12,Ffor short-term contracts, maybe half a
OL,13,Fseason, while they wait for something
OL,14,Fdifferent."
OL,16,FOne of those to make the move over is
OL,17,F18-year-old Callum McCarthy, who just
OL,18,Fjoined Alderney for a year ahead of
OL,19,Fmoving to the United States to study.
