OL,3,CWould you move to this 'tiny island'
OL,4,Cto play football at The Arsenal?
OL,6,FHe says: "I saw the opportunity to
OL,7,Fcome here and work while playing
OL,8,Ffootball, so I thought it was a no-
OL,9,Fbrainer.
OL,11,F"You can gain experience and play
OL,12,Fcompetitively, getting your games
OL,13,Frecorded and being able to watch over
OL,14,Fwhat you've done in a match. You can
OL,15,Fjust learn a lot from being here and
OL,16,Funderstanding the game."
OL,18,FWhile comparisons with the Premier
OL,19,FLeague may end at the island's ground
OL,20,Fname, The Arsenal, club captain Andy
OL,21,FAdamson says it can be a place to grow.
