OL,3,CWould you move to this 'tiny island'
OL,4,Cto play football at The Arsenal?
OL,6,FHe explains: "We can offer a lot,
OL,7,Fmaybe not on the wages, but living on
OL,8,FAlderney is always quite good fun.
OL,10,F"Together as a group, we've shown over
OL,11,Fthe past few years that not only do we
OL,12,Fhave a laugh, but we also compete.
OL,14,F"We're not looking for superstars,
OL,15,Fwe're looking for people that want to
OL,16,Fbe there every week that we can count
OL,17,Fon."
